<topic template="Default" lasteditedby="rbwinst-pr" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="../helpproject.xsd">
  <title translate="true">Initial Grid Dialog Box</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading2_atoc_"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Initial Grid Dialog Box</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Initial Grid</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> dialog box is used to specify the grid for a new ModelMuse MODFLOW</text><conditional-text type="IF" value="FOOTPRINT"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">,</text><conditional-text type="ELSE"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> or</text><conditional-text type="END"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> PHAST</text><conditional-text type="IF" value="FOOTPRINT"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">, or Footprint</text><conditional-text type="END"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> project either when first starting ModelMuse or by selecting </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">File|New</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">. &#160;Its appearance varies slightly depending on whether the user is creating a new </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Initial_Grid_Dialog_Box_for_MO" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">MODFLOW</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> model</text><conditional-text type="IF" value="FOOTPRINT"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">,</text><conditional-text type="ELSE"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> or</text><conditional-text type="END"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> a new </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Initial_Grid_Dialog_Box_for_PH" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">PHAST</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> model</text><conditional-text type="IF" value="FOOTPRINT"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> or a new </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Initial_Grid_Dialog_Box_for_Fo" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Footprint</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> project</text><conditional-text type="END"/><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Clicking the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">Finish</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> button will create a grid with the dimensions and location specified. &#160;If the </text><text styleclass="Normal" style="font-weight:bold;" translate="true">No grid</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> button is clicked instead, a new project will be created without a grid. &#160;The grid can be created later using the methods described in </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="Generating_Grids" styleclass="Normal" translate="true">Generating Grids</link><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">.</text></para>
  </body>
</topic>
